 To properly proposemarriage, a man must possess a steady income, an adequate supply of respect and love, and proper personal appearance. Prior to the beginning of the Love Revolution, a man must acquire his future bridesmaids through social manipulation and/or by purchasing a sufficient supply of cosmetic products. The process of purchasing a sufficient supply of cosmetic products is less obvious in modern times, and the process of social manipulation has shifted to the more subjective feelings of love, admiration, adoration and respect
